[I] A tiny X11 cursor theme

[T] Miniature is a tiny X11 cursor theme ported from a Windows cursor theme.

[U] https://github.com/nxll/miniature

[A] nxll
[M] The T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

[C] extra/theme
[F] CROSS

[L] Unknown
